\,N_G(P)/P\cong H\leq Aut(P)\,
\,|Aut(P)|=p^{n-1}(p-1)\,\,,\,\,\left|N_G(P)/P\right|=a'\,\,,\,\,a'\mid a\Longrightarrow 
